    "attributes": {
        "action": "All worker's rights to be enforceable after 6 months, not 2 years. ",
        "additional_details": "I believe given Covid-19 job losses employees are in a less favourable position then the employers. \r\n\r\nWith a 2 year wait to gain full worker's rights, this can prolong mental abuse from managers and business, by knowing they are more protected then the employees.",
        "background": "Reduce the 2 years requirement on some workers rights to 6 months, in light of Covid-19",
